==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Derne
<hw>Derne</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>dyrnan</ets> to hide. See <er>Dern</er>, <pos>a.</pos>,
<er>Dearn</er>, <pos>a.</pos>]</ety> <def>To hide; to skulk.</def>
<mark>[Scot.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He at length escaped them by <qex>derning</qex> himself in a
foxearth.</q> <rj><qau>H. Miller.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dernful</ent>⟦br⟧
